4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning methods for solving a computer vision problem. 
5. cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as the paper deals with computer vision problems such as depth and ego-motion estimation.
